data.description: Immaculate townhome unit in exceptional condition, ideal for a first-time homebuyer. Spacious primary suite accommodates a king-size bed, featuring an open floor plan, granite countertops with an island, white kitchen, soaking tub, stainless steel appliances, and faux blinds. Double vanity complemented by a walk-in closet, with a conveniently located laundry room on the 2nd level. Total electric unit with a one-car garage equipped with a garage opener. Situated less than 10 minutes from Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport, and just a short 5-minute drive from shopping centers and gyms.
